{"tid":1240261,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我男朋友好煩 逼到我想死","createTime":"2019-06-18T09:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T09:57:37.000Z","uid":68090,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ac63ddaa19f76e5ef8a67884398d7aae8d40c0e0","tid":1240261,"uid":68090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:50:06.000Z","msg":"男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你出面係咪有第二個？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我出面無第二個...我一直都咁愛你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：仲講大話? 好多人話我聽你偷食，有晒證據<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: ...我中出左條女，但條女無大肚喎...咁叫偷食?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 咁都唔係? 你俾個交代我得唔得呀? 係咪男人黎?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我為我既行為道歉，但係我三年內都唔想同你分手，期間我唔會再偷食，但我唔保證你下任男朋友會唔會偷食架喎。你都唔好再發脾氣啦，如果你提分手，我會話俾你老豆老母同我屋企人聽你打我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我罵你咋喎...邊有打你呀?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 你有咩問題再同佢地講啦，BYE<br />\n<br />\n點算好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同左我老豆老母講 佢地又唔聽<br />\n同我男朋友老豆老母講 佢地又將個波踢黎踢去<br />\n條仔仲要做我男朋友三年 點忍..."},{"pid":"fdbfa45333d8e5bdde4761e794200cb64527c983","tid":1240261,"uid":30201,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"其實佢係你呀媽"},{"pid":"8a28200eef77a7e03b396d06ce37a0497d8b29d3","tid":1240261,"uid":20066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:54:13.000Z","msg":"我估冇睇記者會個堆唔會明"},{"pid":"272e975afbe234d60cdc0748e3f75904b5a162b0","tid":1240261,"uid":194912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:55:29.000Z","msg":"就算明都覺得尷尬..."},{"pid":"98c5be1699b36b7f0803ad210f1055721311453a","tid":1240261,"uid":68090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a28200eef77a7e03b396d06ce37a0497d8b29d3","tid":1240261,"uid":20066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:54:13.000Z","msg":"我估冇睇記者會個堆唔會明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:56:04.000Z","msg":"D負評係咪睇唔明我男朋友講咩?<br />\n因為我都唔明我男朋友講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef8e5a8a4e62f4de49f934265e6582a4d06d07c","tid":1240261,"uid":258920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T09:57:37.000Z","msg":"太曲啦師傅..."}]}